    <p class="lead text-muted">Your trusted partner in learning safe and responsible driving.</p>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title text-success">Experienced Instructors</h3>
                    <p class="card-text">Our certified instructors are here to guide you every step of the way.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
